DrqI AkwS nUM AwpxI s`iqAw nwl itkw r`Kx vwlw prmwqmw (ijs jIv nUM mwieAw-moh Awidk qoN bcWdw hY aus dy) ihrdy ivc itk ky aus dy srIr nUM Awpxy rihx leI Gr bxw lYNdw hY (Bwv, aus dy AMdr Awpxw Awp prgt krdw hY) ]1]
hy sMq jno! gurU dy snmuK kr ky gurU dy Sbd ivc joV ky prmwqmw byAMq lukweI nUM (haumY mmqw kwmwidk qoN) bcWdw (cilAw Aw irhw) hY ]1] rhwau]
hy pRBU! (gurU dI rwhIN ijs mnu`K dw qUM au~Dwr krdw hYN) auh Apx`q nUM (Awpxy AMdroN) mwr ky haumY nUM BI mukw lYNdw hY, qy aus nUM ies iqR-BvnI jgq ivc qyrI hI joiq nzrIN AwauNdI hY ]2]
(hy pRBU! ijs jIv nUM qUM qwrdw hYN) auh gurU dy Sbd dI rwhIN au~cI ivcwr dw mwlk ho ky Awpxy mn dy mwiek PurinAW nUM mukw ky (qyrI Xwd nUM) Awpxy mn ivc itkWdw hY ]3]
(hy pRBU! ijs auqy qyrI myhr huMdI hY auh hY Asl jogI, aus dI) surq qyry nws-rihq srUp ivc itkdI hY (ieh, mwno, aus dy AMdr jogI vwlI) isM|I v`jdI hY, aus nUM hryk srIr ivc qyrI hI joiq id`sdI hY (auh iksy nUM iqAwg ky jMglIN phwVIN nhIN Btkdw) ]4]
(gurU dy Sbd ivc itikAw hoieAw mnu`K Asl jogI hY,) auh Awpxy mn nUM aus prmwqmw ivc joVI r`Kdw hY ijs ivc jgq-rcnw dI bIxw sdw v`j rhI hY, auh Awpxy AMdr r`bI joiq cMgI qrHW jgw lYNdw hY ]5]
(hy AauDU! ijs mnu`K nUM prmwqmw gurU dI srn pw ky Awqm-au~Dwr dy rsqy pWdw hY) auh mnu`K ies pMj-q`qI mnu`Kw srIr nUM hwsl kr ky (jMglIN phwVIN jw ky ies nUM suAwh ivc nhIN roldw, auh qW) byAMq prmwqmw dI piv`qr joiq dw dIvw idn rwq (Awpxy AMdr jgweI r`Kdw hY) ]6]
(hy AauDU! pRBU dI ikrpw dw pwqr bixAw hoieAw mnu`K Awpxy ies srIr nUM ikMgurI bxWdw hY, suAws suAws nwm jpx nUM ies srIr-ikMgurI dy qUMby bxWdw hY, aus dy AMdr gurU dw Sbd AnoKI iK`c nwl v`jdw hY (Bwv, gurU dw Sbd aus dy AMdr suAwdlw pRym-rwg pYdw krdw hY) ]7]
